Class KB

  • java.lang.Object
    • amie.data.KB

  • public class KB
extends java.lang.Object
    Class KB This class implements an in-memory knowledge base (KB) for facts without identifiers. It supports a series of conjunctive queries.
    Author:
    Fabian M. Suchanek
